examples.en: He is nearly deaf - never picks his ears.
examples.ru: Он почти глухой - уши совсем не чистит.

examples.en: He picks up the receiver of a nearby phone.
They used picks and sledges to break the rocks.
examples.ru: Камни они разбивали кирками и кувалдами.

examples.en: The microphone picks everything up, and transmits it regardless.
